Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:55.02,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:58.71,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
